            </div>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Environment Variables</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Set these in a <code class="bg-gray-800 px-1 rounded text-xs">.env</code> file for CI/CD or automated workflows:</p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
              <table class="w-full text-left text-sm text-gray-400">
                <thead class="bg-white/5 text-gray-200 font-medium">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="px-4 py-3">Variable</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-3">Description</th>
                  </tr>
